{"tid":2110590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[每個部門把尺都唔同]食環回覆渣哥 指引無話唔俾係餐廳等外賣","createTime":"2020-07-16T04:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T08:43:49.000Z","uid":22556,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"36a39b167647398b47f430bb11e822a5be8f4259","tid":2110590,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:34:13.000Z","msg":"因為又有消息話食環署否認，所以我哋一直不停追問食環署，應該白紙黑字講清楚關於：<br />\n是否禁止客人6點後店內等外賣？<br />\n員工6點後在店内進食是否犯法？<br />\n<br />\n食環署剛剛終於肯回覆：<br />\n暫時內部指引無話禁止食客響舖內等取外賣，但就必須配帶口罩/探熱/限聚1.5米距離，其他詳細指引今日稍後會有公佈。<br />\n<br />\n我哋會繼續追，追到佢哋白紙黑字清清楚楚交待為止😡<br />\n<br />\n垃圾政府無人性，無個部門靠得住🤬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/611333408944704/posts/3244451948966157/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F611333408944704%2Fposts%2F3244451948966157%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n34MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=e562bb55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/611333408944704/posts/3244451948966157/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"58b3d4ca223fcf6203ab98c7f66d2922fee91012","tid":2110590,"uid":20352,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:35:46.000Z","msg":"M記外賣係咪要外面等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477f30913eb78a14eec559b7ca80ace8da0db36e","tid":2110590,"uid":264871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:44:18.000Z","msg":"食環署想做嘢，大家一人一電話打去投訴其他藍店吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8c6f3a9010ab55d41bf220cf1eff23a63c1ddc","tid":2110590,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:45:47.000Z","msg":"仲敢屌人無人性？"},{"pid":"2b0eb6a19f6a462f0caf3259f8aeeefd7ce71e4c","tid":2110590,"uid":240149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T08:43:49.000Z","msg":"[突發](有圖)點解唔撐拎得/lingduck<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2112313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\